259
00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:28,440
<i>¿Qué hace?</i>

260
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:31,750
<i>¿Por qué diablos está contando?</i>

261
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:36,450
Un, dos tres... Un, dos, tres...


262
00:17:36,450 --> 00:17:40,430
Increíble, Kyon-Kyon @controló
